VALUES ('B2_U8_B2_I1', 'ingles-b2-U8', 6, 'multiple_choice_cloze', 'Choose the correct word to fill in the blanks based on the context of media and communication.', '{"prompt_es":"Choose the correct word to fill in the blanks based on the context of media and communication.","mastery_tag":"vocabulary:b2-media","main_text":"In today''s world, the role of (1)[GAP 1] has become pivotal in shaping public opinion. With the rise of social media platforms, (2)[GAP 2] has transformed from traditional print to instantaneous digital updates. Many journalists now rely on (3)[GAP 3] to gather information quickly. Moreover, the (4)[GAP 4] of news has changed dramatically, requiring media outlets to adapt to a fast-paced environment. Finally, the importance of (5)[GAP 5] in journalism cannot be overstated, as it ensures accuracy and credibility.","gaps":[{"id":"1","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"advertising"},{"id":"o2","text":"journalism"},{"id":"o3","text":"television"},{"id":"o4","text":"broadcasting"}]},{"id":"2","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"communication"},{"id":"o2","text":"journalism"},{"id":"o3","text":"broadcasting"},{"id":"o4","text":"media"}]},{"id":"3","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"technology"},{"id":"o2","text":"communication"},{"id":"o3","text":"broadcasting"},{"id":"o4","text":"print"}]},{"id":"4","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"delivery"},{"id":"o2","text":"format"},{"id":"o3","text":"broadcasting"},{"id":"o4","text":"reporting"}]},{"id":"5","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"accuracy"},{"id":"o2","text":"journalism"},{"id":"o3","text":"advertising"},{"id":"o4","text":"reporting"}]}],"correct_answer":{"1":"o2","2":"o2","3":"o1","4":"o1","5":"o1"},"explanation":"(1) El periodismo juega un papel fundamental en la formación de la opinión pública.\n(2) El periodismo se ha transformado de lo impreso a lo digital de manera instantánea.\n(3) La tecnología es esencial para que los periodistas obtengan información rápidamente.\n(4) La entrega de noticias ha cambiado dramáticamente en los últimos años.\n(5) La precisión es crucial en el periodismo para mantener la credibilidad.","complexity":3,"concept_tags":["vocabulary","media","unit","grammar"]}')
