VALUES ('B2_U12_B1_I1', 'ingles-b2-U12', 1, 'fill_blanks', 'Fill in the blanks with the appropriate words to complete the review.', '{"prompt_es":"Fill in the blanks with the appropriate words to complete the review.","mastery_tag":"writing:b2-reviews-articles","main_text":"Last weekend, I visited a new Italian restaurant called ''La Dolce Vita''. The atmosphere was very ___(1)___ and inviting. The staff were polite and ___(2)___, making sure we had everything we needed. I ordered the spaghetti carbonara, which was absolutely ___(3)___. The flavors were rich and the pasta was cooked to ___(4)___. My friend had the tiramisu for dessert; it was a perfect ___(5)___. I highly recommend this restaurant for anyone who loves good Italian food.","correct_answer":["cozy","attentive","delicious","perfection","ending"],"explanation":"(1) La palabra ''cozy'' se utiliza para describir un lugar que es cálido y acogedor.\n(2) La palabra ''attentive'' se refiere a alguien que presta atención a las necesidades de los clientes.\n(3) Utilizamos ''delicious'' para describir algo que tiene un sabor muy bueno.\n(4) La palabra ''perfection'' denota que la pasta estaba cocinada de manera ideal.\n(5) La palabra ''ending'' se utiliza para referirse a la conclusión de una comida o experiencia.","complexity":3,"concept_tags":["writing","reviews","articles","unit"]}')
