VALUES ('B2_U23_B2_I1', 'ingles-b2-U23', 6, 'fill_blanks', 'Complete the sentences with the correct words related to lectures and presentations.', '{"prompt_es":"Complete the sentences with the correct words related to lectures and presentations.","mastery_tag":"listening:b2-lectures","main_text":"When attending a lecture, it is important to take (1)___ to help remember key points. (2)___ are often used to illustrate concepts and engage the audience. The lecturer usually provides a (3)___ at the beginning to outline the main ideas. Effective (4)___ can greatly enhance the delivery of a presentation. Lastly, during the Q&A session, students should feel free to (5)___ any unclear points.","correct_answer":["notes","visuals","overview","communication","ask"],"explanation":"(1) Es importante tomar notas durante una conferencia para recordar los puntos clave.\n(2) Los recursos visuales son útiles para ilustrar conceptos durante las presentaciones.\n(3) Una visión general ayuda a los estudiantes a entender qué esperar de la conferencia.\n(4) La comunicación efectiva es crucial para transmitir ideas claramente.\n(5) Es importante que los estudiantes hagan preguntas para aclarar dudas.","complexity":3,"concept_tags":["listening","lectures","unit"]}')
